                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/ep6-security/login-form-authenticator.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>To use Guard - no matter <em>what</em> crazy authentication system you have - the first
step is always to create an authenticator class. Create a new directory called <code>Security</code>
and inside, a new class: how about <code>LoginFormAuthenticator</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="9efe721a03">
