<p>In reality, this grabs the <code>form.factory</code> service and calls <code>create()</code> on it.</p>
<h2 id="dependency-inject-form-factory-formfactory">Dependency Inject form.factory (FormFactory) <a class="headerlink" href="login-form-authenticator#dependency-inject-form-factory-formfactory" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>So how can we create a form in the authenticator? Use dependency injection to inject
the <code>form.factory</code> service.</p>
<p>Add a <code>__construct()</code> method with a <code>$formFactory</code> argument:</p>
