<p>Normally, we would check if <code>$form-&gt;isValid()</code>, but we'll do any password checking
or other validation manually in a moment. Instead, just skip to <code>$data = $form-&gt;getData()</code>
and <code>return $data</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="9c7e1e528b">
