</p>
<p>Since our form is not bound to a class, this returns an associative array with
<code>_username</code> and <code>_password</code>. And that's it for <code>getCredentials()</code>. If you return
<em>any</em> non-null value, authentication continues to the next step.</p>

    
                        </div>
